Isn't it okay to hate me?

266
00:21:38,031 --> 00:21:40,466
(Momoko) I hated it.

267
00:21:40,533 --> 00:21:42,969
>> Huh?

268
00:21:43,036 --> 00:21:48,975
(Momoko) Fiance, the daughter of a hotel group, etc.→

269
00:21:49,042 --> 00:21:52,478
Take out all the cards I don't have →

270
00:21:52,545 --> 00:21:57,050
I hated Inri-san who appeared next to Min-seok-san.

271
00:21:59,552 --> 00:22:03,990
People come to me asking me to break up →

272
00:22:04,057 --> 00:22:09,062
It's true that I don't understand what it means, that it's scary, and that I hate it.

273
00:22:11,064 --> 00:22:13,499
But →

274
00:22:13,566 --> 00:22:18,571
I was wondering what made you do that.

275
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:32,518
(Momoko) Probably the same as me.

276
00:22:32,585 --> 00:22:34,087
>> Huh?

277
00:22:37,023 --> 00:22:40,526
(Momoko) You like Minseok, right?

278
00:22:42,528 --> 00:22:44,964
That's why I want to be by your side →

279
00:22:45,031 --> 00:22:49,535
You really wanted to protect his future, didn't you?

280
00:22:51,037 --> 00:22:53,473
Are you →

281
00:22:53,539 --> 00:22:58,478
Even after Minseok lost the support of his family →

282
00:22:58,544 --> 00:23:01,981
