283
00:23:02,048 --> 00:23:07,987
It's not because I look at you by title →

284
00:23:08,054 --> 00:23:11,557
I thought it was because I liked him as a person.

285
00:23:13,059 --> 00:23:15,995
Eri-san →

286
00:23:16,062 --> 00:23:21,067
He's a person who really sees what's inside people.

287
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:28,007
(Momoko) Then a little →

288
00:23:28,074 --> 00:23:30,510
I felt like we could become friends.

289
00:23:30,576 --> 00:23:40,953
♪～

290
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:43,956
(Momoko) Would you like something to drink?

291
00:23:44,023 --> 00:23:47,460
Actually, the beer is chilled.

292
00:23:47,527 --> 00:23:50,029
>> Sorry.

293
00:23:52,031 --> 00:23:54,967
I... I'm sorry.

294
00:23:55,034 --> 00:23:57,470
(Momoko) What happened?

295
00:23:57,537 --> 00:23:59,472
>> I don't understand...

296
00:23:59,539 --> 00:24:01,974
(Momoko) Eri-san, let's sit down for a moment, okay?

297
00:24:02,041 --> 00:24:04,043
This way.

298
00:24:05,545 --> 00:24:06,979
please.

299
00:24:07,046 --> 00:24:12,985
(cry)

300
00:24:13,052 --> 00:24:15,555
(Momoko) Yes. (crying)

301
00:24:18,558 --> 00:24:21,494
I was jealous.

302
00:24:21,561 --> 00:24:23,563
you.

303
00:24:26,566 --> 00:24:29,502
So →

304
00:24:29,569 --> 00:24:34,006
I did some mean things.

305
00:24:34,073 --> 00:24:36,008
sorry.

306
00:24:38,511 --> 00:24:46,953
(cry)

307
