This is my first time doing something like this.

308
00:24:50,022 --> 00:24:51,958
(Momoko) Huh?

309
00:24:52,024 --> 00:24:55,027
>> I can make friends with ordinary people.

310
00:24:57,530 --> 00:25:02,468
(Momoko) I see, common people...

311
00:25:02,535 --> 00:25:04,537
Well, that's fine though.

312
00:25:14,547 --> 00:25:20,486
📱(vibration sound)

313
00:25:20,553 --> 00:25:22,555
