322
00:34:49,455 --> 00:34:52,391
It's late for lunch, so would you like some soba?

323
00:34:52,458 --> 00:34:54,893
(Mika) That's good. (Momoko) Oh! Then I'll call you.

324
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,962
