327
00:35:11,443 --> 00:35:13,879
(Momoko) Yes.

328
00:35:13,946 --> 00:35:15,881
>> Huh, where are you going?

329
00:35:15,948 --> 00:35:18,383
What about soba? >> It's okay, it's okay.

330
00:35:18,450 --> 00:35:20,886
Director, do you know? Where did you go?

331
00:35:20,953 --> 00:35:24,890
Mika-chan has a refreshingly insensitive ability.

332
