Why? What do you mean?

334
00:35:35,467 --> 00:35:37,469
(Momoko) Minseok!

335
00:35:44,476 --> 00:35:46,411
(Momoko) I'm sorry.

336
00:35:46,478 --> 00:35:50,482
The words I cherished the most...

337
00:35:52,985 --> 00:35:55,420
I've always wanted to apologize because I lied.

338
00:35:55,487 --> 00:35:57,489
But I...

339
