353
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:44,896
(Minseok) I can understand simple Japanese. (Momoko) Ah.

354
00:37:44,963 --> 00:37:46,898
>>Then let's sit down.

355
00:37:46,965 --> 00:37:48,967
(Momoko) Yes.

356
