364
00:38:19,931 --> 00:38:21,867
(Minseok) ``It's a nice shop,'' he said.

365
00:38:21,933 --> 00:38:24,870
(Momoko) Well, it definitely wasn't that kind of nuance.

366
00:38:24,936 --> 00:38:28,373
(Minseok) Ah, no, “Thank you for introducing me to a good restaurant →

367
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:30,942
I'm really grateful.''

368
00:38:36,948 --> 00:38:39,384
(Momoko) Huh? What what? (Minseok) Ugh.

369
00:38:39,451 --> 00:38:42,888
>>My brother loves you very much.

370
00:38:42,954 --> 00:38:44,890
Thank you for your continued support.

371
00:38:44,956 --> 00:38:46,892
(Momoko) Yeah!

372
00:38:46,958 --> 00:38:49,895
No! Hahaha...

373
00:38:49,961 --> 00:38:53,965
Hehehe... already.

374
00:38:59,971 --> 00:39:05,977
(Jung Hoon) [Kim Min Seok]

375
00:39:07,479 --> 00:39:09,414
