394
00:41:22,414 --> 00:41:25,851
(Minseok) "What do you think is the first word I learned in Korea?"

395
00:41:25,917 --> 00:41:28,920
(Momoko) What? (Minseok) Eh, I don't remember either.

396
00:41:33,925 --> 00:41:36,361
(Minseok) Ah~｡ (Momoko) What?

397
