(Minseok) It means "Let's do it together." (Momoko) Ah.

398
00:41:42,434 --> 00:41:45,370
(Minseok) It's my brother's favorite phrase, so I've learned it too.

399
00:41:45,437 --> 00:41:46,872
(Momoko) I see.

400
00:41:46,938 --> 00:41:50,942
>>Always together I was always next to my younger brother.

401
00:41:57,949 --> 00:41:59,885
(Minseok) If I don't have you, I'll...

402
00:41:59,951 --> 00:42:02,888
