(Minseok) How did you know? (Momoko) Huh? Did you get it right?

404
00:42:05,457 --> 00:42:07,893
(Minseok) Yeah. (Momoko) I think I'm starting to understand something.

405
00:42:07,959 --> 00:42:09,895
>> Amazing. (Momoko) Amazing.

406
00:42:09,961 --> 00:42:11,897
>> That's amazing. (Momoko) Oh, that's amazing.

407
00:42:11,963 --> 00:42:14,399
📱(vibration sound)

408
00:42:14,466 --> 00:42:16,902
